Create a topic page with a suitable WikiWord name. Edit in the WikiWord name on any page you want to belong to the topic. Going to the topic page and clicking on the title link finds all pages that have the topic link on them. A given page can be assigned any number of topics.



Clicking on the title of this page finds all pages assigned the TopicSearch topic.http://localhost/wiki/wiki.rb?mode=search&search=TopicSearch
